description: An astonishing afternoon: Dan Morgenstern told stories -- true and first-hand -- to my video camera and to you.  If you don't know Mister Morgenstern, you need to brush up on your Jazzspeare.  Recorded on March 3, 2017, at Dan's home, by Michael Steinman for JAZZ LIVES (http://www.jazzlives.wordpress.com)
